<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Form Submission Confirmation - Medh Learning Platform</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      padding: 40px 20px;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 650px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a6cf7 0%, #667eea 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    .header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 20"><defs><radialGradient id="a" cx=".66" cy=".30" r=".7"><stop offset="0" stop-color="%23ffffff" stop-opacity=".2"/><stop offset=".5" stop-color="%23ffffff" stop-opacity=".05"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="%23ffffff" stop-opacity="0"/></radialGradient></defs><rect width="100" height="20" fill="url(%23a)"/></svg>');
      opacity: 0.3;
    }
    .header-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .header-subtitle {
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9;
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    .success-icon {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin: 20px 0 10px;
      display: block;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .confirmation-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e8 0%, #f0fff0 100%);
      border: 2px solid #4caf50;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .confirmation-title {
      color: #2e7d32;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .confirmation-message {
      color: #388e3c;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .form-details {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .details-header {
      color: #2d3748;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .details-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 15px;
    }
    .detail-item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border-left: 4px solid #4a6cf7;
    }
    .detail-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #4a5568;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .detail-value {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #2d3748;
      text-align: right;
      max-width: 60%;
      word-break: break-word;
    }
    .message-preview {
      background: #fff5f5;
      border-left: 4px solid #fc8181;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    }
    .message-preview h4 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      color: #c53030;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .message-preview p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #744210;
      font-style: italic;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .next-steps {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e6f3ff 0%, #f0f8ff 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .next-steps h3 {
      color: #1e40af;
      margin: 0 0 15px;
      font-size: 18px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .next-steps ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: #1e3a8a;
    }
    .next-steps li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .action-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      min-width: 150px;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a6cf7 0%, #667eea 100%);
      color: white;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b5cf0 0%, #5a67d8 100%);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(74, 108, 247, 0.3);
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: white;
      color: #4a6cf7;
      border: 2px solid #4a6cf7;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #4a6cf7;
      color: white;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(74, 108, 247, 0.2);
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f7fafc;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      color: #718096;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #4a6cf7;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .social-links {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .social-links a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 10px;
      color: #718096;
      font-size: 18px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .social-links a:hover {
      color: #4a6cf7;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-wrapper {
        padding: 20px 10px;
      }
      .container {
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .header, .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      .action-buttons {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .btn {
        min-width: auto;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 280px;
      }
      .detail-item {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 5px;
      }
      .detail-value {
        text-align: left;
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="header-content">
          <div class="logo">üìö Medh Learning Platform</div>
          <div class="header-subtitle">Form Submission Confirmation</div>
          <div class="success-icon">‚úÖ</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <div class="confirmation-section">
          <div class="confirmation-title">
            <span>üéâ</span>
            Form Submitted Successfully!
          </div>
          <div class="confirmation-message">
            Thank you for submitting your {{form_type}} form. We have received your information and will get back to you soon.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-details">
          <div class="details-header">
            <span>üìã</span>
            Submission Details
          </div>
          <div class="details-grid">
            <div class="detail-item">
              <div class="detail-label">Form ID</div>
              <div class="detail-value">{{form_id}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
              <div class="detail-label">Form Type</div>
              <div class="detail-value">{{form_type}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
              <div class="detail-label">Name</div>
              <div class="detail-value">{{name}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
              <div class="detail-label">Submitted On</div>
              <div class="detail-value">{{formatDate submitted_at "full"}}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {{#if message}}
        <div class="message-preview">
          <h4>üìù Your Message Preview</h4>
          <p>"{{message}}"</p>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="next-steps">
          <h3>
            <span>üöÄ</span>
            What Happens Next?
          </h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Our team will review your submission within 24-48 hours</li>
            <li>You'll receive a follow-up email with next steps</li>
            <li>For urgent inquiries, you can contact us directly</li>
            <li>Keep this email for your records</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="action-buttons">
          <a href="{{dashboard_url}}" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Dashboard</a>
          <a href="{{contact_url}}" class="btn btn-secondary">Contact Support</a>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px; background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #4a6cf7;">
          <strong>üí° Need Help?</strong> If you have any questions about your submission or need immediate assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@medh.co" style="color: #4a6cf7;">support@medh.co</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p><strong>Medh Learning Platform</strong></p>
        <p>Empowering the next generation of learners</p>
        
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="#" title="Facebook">üìò</a>
          <a href="#" title="Twitter">üê¶</a>
          <a href="#" title="LinkedIn">üíº</a>
          <a href="#" title="Instagram">üì∏</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>
          <a href="{{privacy_url}}">Privacy Policy</a> | 
          <a href="{{terms_url}}">Terms of Service</a> | 
          <a href="{{unsubscribe_url}}">Unsubscribe</a>
        </p>
        
        <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Medh Learning Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 